It's late fall and it's time for golden rice to ripen and harvest. 
When I see yellow, I think of the sun in the universe, and I think of golden colors as wide as rice here. 
Like the sun, like the rice. 

It's a small but big.
Two.

여기 벼처럼 넓은 황금빛도 생각해.

before eternal sleep comes,

2023. 11. 7 - 12. 8 

East Atelier gallery Seoul 

Before you sleep forever, I saw you.
Here's what you looked like when you were born.
In color, what color have you been since birth.
I can see the color on you now.
I saw your color and it spread from you.
Your color is going from light to dark.
Your color is fading from dark and falling asleep.

I happened to see you next to Jongmyo Shrine.

.
.
.
